# Windows System Admin Toolkit

This project is a Windows system administration script designed to automate common admin tasks using Python. The script was created as part of a lab assignment and includes both required tasks and custom additions to enhance functionality.

## ðŸ›  Features

Implemented tasks:

- `--task win-events` - Triages Windows Security log (4624/4625).
- `--task win-pkgs` - Lists installed software (optional CSV export).
- `--task win-services` - Checks and restarts critical services.
- `--task win-uptime` (NEW) - Displays system uptime based on `net statistics workstation`.
- `--task win-startup` (NEW) - Lists startup programs from the Windows Registry (`HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run`).

